      "role": "user",
      "content": "it feels like the lights went out. i used to see everything in color, every shadow had a meaning, every stroke on the canvas felt like i was finally breathing. but now... it's just gray. i look at my hands and they don't feel like mine anymore. there's nothing inside. just this heavy, hollow space where the music used to be. i feel like a ghost haunting my own skin.",
